://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 680, \"end\": 684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7184322465615356e-37, \"text\": \"Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel so completely grateful to have been asked to open the Paris @Olympics 2024 this year,\\\" she shared.\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 813, \"end\": 818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.546955749510603e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her performance, which celebrated French art, music, and theatre, was a tribute to the country's rich cultural heritage, according to theNew York Post.\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 893, \"end\": 899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9975220372568128, \"rank\": 0.0024834091457080903, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The singer chose to performMon Truc en Plumes, a classic French song famously sung by Zizi Jeanmaire.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1069, \"end\": 1075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9975220372568128, \"rank\": 0.0024834091457080903, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1098, \"end\": 1112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zizi_Jeanmaire\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zizi Jeanmaire\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zizi_Jeanmaire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zizi_Jeanmaire\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gaga's connection to the song is personal and profound.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1114, \"end\": 1118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7184322465615356e-37, \"text\": \"Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Although I am not a French artist, I have always felt a very special connection with French people and singing French music,\\\" she noted.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1192, \"end\": 1198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9975220372568128, \"rank\": 0.0024834091457080903, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1257, \"end\": 1270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 1283, \"end\": 1289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9975220372568128, \"rank\": 0.0024834091457080903, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The song, which translates to 'My Thing with Feathers,' honours the legacy of Jeanmaire.\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This a French ballerina and a key figure in French musical history.\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1406, \"end\": 1412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9975220372568128, \"rank\": 0.0024834091457080903, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1443, \"end\": 1449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9975220372568128, \"rank\": 0.0024834091457080903, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gaga's performance combined traditional and modern elements to create something truly spectacular.\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1566, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1468, \"end\": 1472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7184322465615356e-37, \"text\": \"Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She collaborated with Dior to design custom costumes featuring naturally molted feathers, reflecting the elegance of French cabaret.\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1685, \"end\": 1691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9975220372568128, \"rank\": 0.0024834091457080903, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, she rented pom poms from the Le Lido archive, a famed French cabaret theatre, according toAP News.\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1814, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1770, \"end\": 1776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9975220372568128, \"rank\": 0.0024834091457080903, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These elements contributed to a performance that was both innovative and deeply rooted in French tradition.\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1923, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1906, \"end\": 1912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9975220372568128, \"rank\": 0.0024834091457080903, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her preparation was equally meticulous.\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 1964, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gaga studied French choreography, blending contemporary dance with classic French styles.\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 2055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1966, \"end\": 1970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7184322465615356e-37, \"text\": \"Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}, {\"begin\": 1979, \"end\": 1985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9975220372568128, \"rank\": 0.0024834091457080903, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2041, \"end\": 2047, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9975220372568128, \"rank\": 0.0024834091457080903, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She dedicated countless hours to rehearsing, a process she described as \\\"tireless.\\\"\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In her post, she fondly recalled her early days, saying, \\\"I bet you did not know I used to dance at a 60's French party on the Lower East Side when I was first starting out!\\\"\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2249, \"end\": 2261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French party\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Party\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gaga's excitement for the Olympics and admiration for the athletes were evident in her performance.\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2318, \"end\": 2322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7184322465615356e-37, \"text\": \"Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Watching the Olympic Games always makes me cry!\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2467, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your talent is unimaginable,\\\" she exclaimed.\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2512, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Herperformancewas not just an entertainment spectacle but also a heartfelt celebration of the Games and the French people, according toSky News.\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2622, \"end\": 2635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In her Instagram post, Gaga also